YARN
--------------------------------------------------
 npm install -g yarn
yarn global add @angular/cli 

ng set --global packageManager=yarn
yarn add <name>   /// same as npm install  <name> --save


--------------------------------------------------
 Lodash
--------------------------------------------------
- a javascript utility library

- Lodash makes JavaScript easier by taking the hassle out of working with arrays,
numbers, objects, strings, etc. Lodashâ€™s modular methods are great for:

- Iterating arrays, objects, & strings
- Manipulating & testing values
- Creating composite functions

use in application by doing this:

import * as _ from 'lodash';

npm install lodash --save
 npm install @types/lodash --save-dev

import * as _ from 'lodash';    // in main.ts so i can use it in the rest of my program











